{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka tu muins taunu ne pa-\ndarri / itt ka mehs tew ne eſtam\nniſkahruſchi / un itt ka mehs tew\nlabbu ween eſtam darrijuschi/ un\ntew ar Meeru atlaidufschi / bet tu\nnu eſti ta KUNGA Swehtihts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiſsch darrija teem\nDſihreſ / un tee ehde un dſehre.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un zehlahs Rihta agri/\nun ſwehreja weens ohtram / un\nIhsiaaks atlaidie tohs / tad gahje\ntee no winna ar Meeru.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tanni Deena nahze\nIhsaaka Kalpi/ un pafazzija win-\nram/ kas ar Akku bij notizzis/ ko\ntee bij rakluschi/ un tee fazzija us\nwinnu : Mehs eſtam Uhdeni at-\nraddufschi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiſsch nosauze to Se-\nbu / tadeht irr ta Pilſfahta\nWahrds Berseba / lihds chai\nDeenai.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Eſaws bija tſchetrdefinitis\nGaddus wezz/un nehine Juditu/\nBerusta Eetitera Meitu par See-\nwu/un Basnatu/Eelona ta Eeti-\ntera Meitu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Untahs padarrija Sirde-\nEhſtus Ihsaakam un Rebekai.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "N tas notikle/ kad Iha-\nsaaks bij wezz tappis /\nun winna Azzis tum-\nschas mettuschees/ ka wiſsch labbi\nne redſeja/ tad aizinaja wiſsch fa-\nnu wezzaku Dehtu Eesawu / un\nfazzija us to: Mans Dehts: Un\ntas atbildeja winnam: Reds/ ſche-\nes efinu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſsch fazzija: Rangi-\njelle / es efinu wezz tappis / es ne-\nfinnu mannas Mirfchanas Dee-\nnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Nemin tad nu luhdſams/\ntawus ( ſtrehlijama ) Rihkus /\ntawu Kohzori/ un tawu Stohpu/\nun aiseij Lankā / un meddi man\nkahdu Medijunn.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un fataiti man gardus\nWirrumus / itt ka es eezeeniju /\nun zell man tohs preekſcha / tad\nes ehdischu / ka tew manna\nDwehſeli fwehti/pirms es mirſtu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Rebekka dsirdeja / ko\nIhsaaks/ us farwu Dehtu Eesawu\nrunnaja / un Eſaws gahje us\nLanku / grippedans kahdn Med-\ndijumu meddiht / ka wiſsch to\neenestu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Rebekka runnaja ar fa-\nwu Dehtu Jehkabu : un fazzija:\nReds/es efinu dsirdeji tawu Teh-\nwu/ us tawu Brahli Eesawu ta-\nrunnjam/ un fakkam:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Atnefs man weenu Meddi-\njumu / un fataiti man gardus\nWirrumus / ka es ehmu / tad es-\ntew fwehtischu ta KUNGA\nPreekſcha/ pirms es mirſtu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un nu mans Dehts paglau-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
